\ ra (deg)
\ ___ right ascension (J2000)
\ dec (deg)
\ ___ declination (J2000)
\ clon
\ ___ Right ascention in Sexagesimal format.
\ clat
\ ___ Declination in Sexagesimal format.
\ sigra (arcsec)
\ ___ uncertainty in RA
\ sigdec (arcsec)
\ ___ uncertainty in DEC
\ sigradec (arcsec)
\ ___ uncertainty cross-term
\ glon (deg)
\ ___ galactic longitude
\ glat (deg)
\ ___ galactic latitude
\ elon (deg)
\ ___ ecliptic longitude
\ elat (deg)
\ ___ ecliptic latitude
\ w1mpro (mag)
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry magnitude, band 1
\ w1sigmpro (mag)
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry flux uncertainty in mag units, band 1
\ w1snr
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry S/N ratio, band 1
\ w1rchi2
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry reduced chi^2, band 1
\ w2mpro (mag)
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry magnitude, band 2
\ w2sigmpro (mag)
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry flux uncertainty in mag units, band 2
\ w2snr
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry S/N ratio, band 2
\ w2rchi2
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry reduced chi^2, band 2
\ rchi2
\ ___ instrumental profile-fit photometry reduced chi squared, total
\ nb
\ ___ number of blend components used in each fit
\ na
\ ___ active deblend flag (=1 if actively deblended)
\ w1sat
\ ___ fraction of pixels saturated, band 1
\ w2sat
\ ___ fraction of pixels saturated, band 2
\ satnum
\ ___ minimum sample at which saturation occurs, 1 char per band
\ cc_flags
\ ___ prioritized artifacts affecting the source in each band
\ det_bit
\ ___ bit-encoded number(10) indicating detection for each band
\ ph_qual
\ ___ photometric quality of each band (A=highest, U=upper limit)
\ sso_flg
\ ___ known solar system object association flag (0=no association,
\ 1=association)
\ qual_frame
\ ___ quality score value for frame
\ qi_fact
\ ___ quality factor qi value for frame: image quality
\ saa_sep (deg)
\ ___ distance from frame center to SAA boundary
\ moon_masked
\ ___ flag (0/1) indicating whether frame is within the moon-mask area in each
\ band
\ w1frtr
\ ___ Transient pixel indicator string, band 1
\ w2frtr
\ ___ Transient pixel indicator string, band 2
\ mjd (mjdate)
\ ___ modified Julian date of the mid-point of the observation of the frame
\ allwise_cntr
\ ___ closest associated ALLWISE Catalog source cntr
\ r_allwise (arcsec)
\ ___ radial offset between NEOWISER src and associated ALLWISE src
\ pa_allwise (deg)
\ ___ position angle (E of N) of vector from NEOWISER src to associated ALLWISE
\ src
\ n_allwise (int)
\ ___ number of ALLWISE src  entries found within search radius of NEOWISER src
\ w1mpro_allwise (mag)
\ ___ W1mpro magnitude  of the associated ALLWISE source
\ w1sigmpro_allwise (mag)
\ ___ W1 photometric uncertainty of the associated ALLWISE  source
\ w2mpro_allwise (mag)
\ ___ W2mpro magnitude  of the associated ALLWISE  source
\ w2sigmpro_allwise (mag)
\ ___ W2 photometric uncertainty of the associated ALLWISE  source
\ w3mpro_allwise (mag)
