\ w4mpro_allwise (mag)
\ ___ W4mpro magnitude  of the associated ALLWISE  source
\ w4sigmpro_allwise (mag)
\ ___ W4 photometric uncertainty of the associated ALLWISE  source
\ dist (arcsec)
\ ___ Distance between the target position and each source in arcsec.
\ angle (deg)
\ ___ Position Angle in degree.
